channel.title: Same Song, Same time, different channel
channel.description:
Around 3:55 Today (3rd august 2007) there was the same song on Scuzz and Kerrang at the same time (almost). The song way by Killswitch engage and was holy driver.
I found that quite weird but at the same time annoying.
Post if something has happened to you like that!
